    {
      "text": "The Note (公開されなかった手記, Koukai Sarenakatta Shuki) is a first-person survival horror adventure game developed by NK System and published by Team Bughouse in Japan and SunSoft in Europe for the Sony PlayStation. It was released in Japan on January 17, 1997; and in Europe on October 1 of the same year. The game was not released in North America.",
